Author: Sebastian Utz <su@rtme.net>
Date:   Thu Sep 26 10:55:58 2024 +0200

    Handle concurrent calls at the QueryProfiler
    
    The QueryProfiler must be thread-safe as it needs to handle concurrent
    access. Otherwise, this may lead to unexpected exception when profiling
    queries using ``EXPLAIN ANALYZE`` statements
    
    Relates to https://github.com/elastic/elasticsearch/commit/947234a8ce2e3fae3605ee7b55075e0787ed986f.
    
    (cherry picked from commit 106436589bb5bde52346e54d66f681117fbc5a8d)
    
    # Conflicts:
    #       docs/appendices/release-notes/5.8.4.rst
    #       server/src/main/java/org/elasticsearch/search/profile/query/QueryProfiler.java

